WEBVTT

01:37.840 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.100 --> 01:43.960
[Episode 34]

01:46.840 --> 01:47.920
Tomorrow at 10 a.m.,

01:47.920 --> 01:49.660
the ribbon-cutting ceremony
will start on time.

01:49.660 --> 01:51.870
All departments must be
on standby by 7 a.m.

01:51.870 --> 01:53.000
By 8 a.m., we need to complete

01:53.000 --> 01:54.870
the final on-site confirmation.

01:56.560 --> 01:59.509
I have an online meeting
with New Zealand tomorrow morning.

01:59.509 --> 02:01.310
As for the preparations
before the opening,

02:01.310 --> 02:02.510
I won't participate.

02:02.640 --> 02:05.200
Is it the bidding for New Zealand's
Yuntian Group?

02:05.200 --> 02:06.000
Yes.

02:07.110 --> 02:08.000
Don't worry.

02:08.000 --> 02:10.330
I'll handle things at the art exhibition.

02:10.870 --> 02:11.750
I'm here.

02:12.150 --> 02:13.950
Let's both do our best tomorrow.

02:14.490 --> 02:15.020
Bye.

02:44.400 --> 02:45.770
Give a tip, sir.

02:48.150 --> 02:48.730
I'll do it.

02:48.730 --> 02:49.400
Let me do it.

02:53.430 --> 02:54.780
Come on, Jizhou.

02:55.430 --> 02:55.960
All right.

02:55.960 --> 02:56.820
That's enough.

03:04.870 --> 03:05.330
Come on.

03:06.560 --> 03:09.000
To your magnificent challenge.

03:09.520 --> 03:09.980
Cheers.

03:18.030 --> 03:19.690
Actually, I'm quite ashamed.

03:20.030 --> 03:21.310
I'm almost 40,

03:21.310 --> 03:25.240
and I'm still wavering and struggling
between different identities.

03:25.680 --> 03:26.740
You know what, Dad?

03:27.120 --> 03:28.250
I really admire you.

03:28.620 --> 03:29.400
When you were young,

03:29.400 --> 03:30.800
you knew what you wanted

03:30.800 --> 03:32.200
and what you wanted to do.

03:32.700 --> 03:34.150
Am I a failure?

03:37.020 --> 03:38.950
I think it's exactly the opposite.

03:39.750 --> 03:41.360
There are two kinds of people.

03:41.360 --> 03:42.290
One kind

03:42.360 --> 03:44.560
only takes one path in their whole life.

03:44.940 --> 03:45.740
The other kind

03:46.040 --> 03:47.430
spends their whole life

03:47.430 --> 03:49.560
exploring countless possibilities.

03:50.120 --> 03:51.180
From the time

03:51.430 --> 03:52.430
you so firmly

03:52.430 --> 03:54.280
refused to inherit my business

03:54.780 --> 03:56.860
and went to study your art instead.

03:57.000 --> 03:58.520
From that moment on,

03:58.829 --> 03:59.770
your destiny

04:00.120 --> 04:02.050
was destined to be an exploration.

04:02.760 --> 04:04.160
An endless exploration.

04:05.560 --> 04:06.710
Don't worry about the process.

04:06.710 --> 04:07.800
Just enjoy it.

04:08.110 --> 04:09.560
Okay, thank you, Dad.

04:10.310 --> 04:11.870
I hope my art exhibition tomorrow

04:11.870 --> 04:13.560
will be a perfect start to

04:13.560 --> 04:15.090
another journey in my life.

04:15.840 --> 04:16.680
But,

04:17.120 --> 04:19.680
you held such an important exhibition

04:19.829 --> 04:21.000
here,

04:22.270 --> 04:25.230
and even lost a large sum of money
in Hong Kong.

04:25.720 --> 04:26.830
Is a big part of the reason

04:26.830 --> 04:28.800
because Miyu is here?

04:32.040 --> 04:34.300
No one knows a son better than his father.

04:35.830 --> 04:37.380
But looking at it now,

04:37.600 --> 04:39.300
I might have

04:39.830 --> 04:41.159
a formidable opponent.

04:42.260 --> 04:44.280
The essence of humanity is competition.

04:44.280 --> 04:45.940
Competition brings joy.

04:46.560 --> 04:47.909
No matter the outcome,

04:48.040 --> 04:49.430
just leave no regrets.

04:50.430 --> 04:51.000
Right?

04:52.710 --> 04:53.170
Cheers.

05:09.220 --> 05:19.030
[Gilded Years,
Tan Jizhou's Shanghai Art Exhibition]

05:27.780 --> 05:31.340
[5:00 Good morning]

06:02.480 --> 06:06.140
[Gilded Years,
Tan Jizhou's Shanghai Art Exhibition]

06:10.980 --> 06:12.760
Don't put these flowers
at the door. They're in the way.

06:12.760 --> 06:13.630
Put them on the side.

06:13.630 --> 06:14.750
Okay, Ms. Xu.

07:57.430 --> 07:58.960
Has Ms. Xu arrived already?

07:59.110 --> 07:59.600
Yes.

08:01.480 --> 08:02.040
Miyu.

08:20.320 --> 08:21.420
What happened?

08:21.600 --> 08:22.870
Didn't we confirm earlier

08:22.870 --> 08:24.470
that there were no problems?

08:25.890 --> 08:27.220
There were no problems.

08:28.040 --> 08:29.830
But the machine broke down at 3 a.m.

08:29.830 --> 08:30.770
I don't know either.

08:30.770 --> 08:32.350
Why didn't you report for repair
when it broke?

08:32.350 --> 08:33.320
Where were the security guards?

08:33.320 --> 08:33.960
Ms. Xu,

08:33.960 --> 08:36.039
we were all following your arrangements.

08:36.039 --> 08:37.600
You didn't check it yourself at night,

08:37.600 --> 08:38.440
and now you blame me.

08:38.440 --> 08:39.030
Enough!

08:41.510 --> 08:43.360
I'm not here to listen to you
shirk your responsibilities.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.250
Ms. Lin,

08:44.510 --> 08:47.080
please believe that we will definitely
get the painting back.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.840
Get it back? How?

08:49.200 --> 08:50.520
Where should we get it back?

08:50.520 --> 08:52.090
There are less than 3 hours left

08:52.090 --> 08:53.680
before the opening ribbon-cutting
ceremony.

08:53.680 --> 08:55.100
Please give us one more chance.

08:55.100 --> 08:56.920
Just admit that you messed it up.

08:57.110 --> 08:58.020
Ms. Xu,

08:58.150 --> 08:59.870
you don't need to make promises to me.

08:59.870 --> 09:01.720
I know you sales people too well.

09:01.760 --> 09:03.290
When trying to get clients,

09:03.390 --> 09:05.180
you flatter like no other.

09:05.270 --> 09:07.980
But once you get them,
you can't control the situation.

09:07.980 --> 09:09.990
I really doubt what level

09:10.010 --> 09:11.250
your hotel considers

09:11.280 --> 09:13.190
our art exhibition to be at.

09:13.390 --> 09:15.940
Are you sincere to us?

09:17.150 --> 09:17.750
I'm sorry.

09:17.760 --> 09:18.980
Say no more.

09:19.550 --> 09:21.890
Due to a hotel security incident,
the exhibition

09:21.890 --> 09:23.620
is facing an indefinite delay.

09:23.870 --> 09:25.840
Ms. Xu, save your words

09:25.840 --> 09:28.110
for the police and the media.

09:28.140 --> 09:29.000
Cindy,

09:29.750 --> 09:30.450
I'm sorry.

09:30.470 --> 09:31.930
I don't agree to postpone.

09:32.260 --> 09:33.560
The reporters are already outside.

09:33.560 --> 09:35.000
If we postpone now,

09:35.030 --> 09:36.530
our reputation will be ruined.

09:36.530 --> 09:38.770
Besides, we still have 3 hours.

09:39.010 --> 09:40.730
Let's find the painting first, okay?

09:40.730 --> 09:43.100
Kevin, to hold the exhibition here,

09:43.250 --> 09:46.260
we've already paid two million
in liquidated damages.

09:46.260 --> 09:48.320
Are you going to gamble
with your art career now

09:48.320 --> 09:49.750
just for this Ms. Xu?

09:56.250 --> 09:58.270
I'm sorry, Cindy is a bit blunt.

09:58.410 --> 09:59.610
I'll persuade her.

09:59.740 --> 10:01.000
I'll leave this to you.

10:11.150 --> 10:11.910
Lu Zhenzhen,

10:12.390 --> 10:13.770
tell me the truth.

10:14.210 --> 10:16.340
Does this have anything to do with you?

10:16.980 --> 10:18.270
Before you start
throwing accusations around,

10:18.270 --> 10:19.660
can you use your brain for once?

10:19.660 --> 10:21.880
We are in the same boat.

10:21.950 --> 10:23.950
What good would doing this do for us?

10:51.270 --> 10:54.240
So satisfying.
I haven't felt this good in a long time.

10:54.110 --> 10:57.710
[Purong Hotel]

10:54.510 --> 10:55.710
This time, we finally

10:55.840 --> 10:57.870
got to vent our anger.

10:59.360 --> 11:00.600
But I still think

11:00.870 --> 11:02.960
it's a risky move after all.

11:03.190 --> 11:05.120
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

11:05.120 --> 11:06.600
If we don't play hardball,

11:06.630 --> 11:08.870
Ji won't know what we're capable of.

11:10.920 --> 11:14.580
[Purong Hotel]

11:11.060 --> 11:13.120
Is the person you found to handle this

11:13.480 --> 11:14.610
actually reliable?

11:15.390 --> 11:17.510
Don't worry, he's very smart.

11:18.360 --> 11:21.080
The surveillance cameras
have been tampered with.

11:21.080 --> 11:22.330
In such a short time,

11:22.480 --> 11:24.680
they won't be able to find the painting.

11:25.390 --> 11:26.640
When the exhibition is over,

11:26.640 --> 11:28.950
we'll put it back secretly.

11:28.980 --> 11:31.440
Then we'll insist

11:31.720 --> 11:33.880
he failed to keep the painting well.

11:34.000 --> 11:35.660
It's a big misunderstanding.

11:36.450 --> 11:37.960
Even if Ji

11:38.000 --> 11:40.000
has the capability to reach the sky,

11:40.890 --> 11:43.200
he will have to take the blame
and get out.

11:46.620 --> 11:47.770
Are you sure they

11:48.390 --> 11:50.990
don't have any loopholes
to exploit this time?

11:51.870 --> 11:52.900
Even if they do,

11:52.950 --> 11:54.920
we still have a backup plan.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.850
Ji is bound to lose this time.

11:57.570 --> 11:59.600
But don't let your guard down.

12:00.350 --> 12:01.860
After such a huge mistake,

12:02.080 --> 12:04.240
Ji Feng hasn't reacted yet.

12:04.600 --> 12:05.930
I think it's not normal.

12:06.280 --> 12:07.950
I heard he was held up early this morning

12:07.950 --> 12:11.040
by some business with Yuntian Group.

12:13.860 --> 12:16.350
Keep a close eye on Xu Miyu.

12:16.420 --> 12:17.370
Don't worry.

12:17.600 --> 12:19.200
Lu Zhenzhen is watching her.

12:20.930 --> 12:22.770
That Lu Zhenzhen under you

12:23.240 --> 12:25.040
has a lot of tricks up her sleeve.

12:25.140 --> 12:26.430
Don't let her sell us out.

12:26.430 --> 12:28.070
Don't worry.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.930
I know what I'm doing.

12:47.870 --> 12:50.200
This time, I want to
rely more on my own efforts.

12:50.200 --> 12:51.840
I don't want to rely on you to help me.

12:51.840 --> 12:54.740
I have an online meeting
with New Zealand tomorrow morning.

12:54.740 --> 12:56.440
I won't participate in the preparations

12:56.440 --> 12:57.570
before the opening.

13:11.440 --> 13:13.150
Miyu, long time no see.

13:13.150 --> 13:13.810
Yin Xiang.

13:14.050 --> 13:15.530
-Qingping. Ke.
-Miss Miyu.

13:15.530 --> 13:16.720
I need you guys.

13:17.030 --> 13:19.150
A painting is missing from
Mr. Tan's exhibition.

13:19.150 --> 13:20.320
I've already checked the hotel's

13:20.320 --> 13:21.750
entrance and exit surveillance.

13:21.750 --> 13:23.540
I think the painting
should still be in the hotel.

13:23.540 --> 13:25.200
Can you guys help me find it?

13:25.550 --> 13:27.080
Then I'll get the sisters
from other floors

13:27.080 --> 13:28.200
to look for it together.

13:28.200 --> 13:30.030
No, the media is already at the hotel.

13:30.030 --> 13:32.080
We absolutely cannot make this public.

13:32.080 --> 13:33.550
As long as it wasn't taken by a guest,

13:33.550 --> 13:35.210
there aren't many places
in the hotel to hide a painting.

13:35.210 --> 13:36.810
We'll search the place again

13:37.040 --> 13:39.040
and let you know if there's any news.

13:40.320 --> 13:40.920
Thank you.

13:46.230 --> 13:47.080
[Tan Jizhou‘s Art Exhibition]

13:47.030 --> 13:47.960
I didn't find it here.

13:47.080 --> 13:48.270
[Yin Xiang]

13:48.550 --> 13:49.870
I don't have it either.

13:48.770 --> 13:50.030
[Ke Wenxue]

13:50.720 --> 13:52.550
What about the electrical room
and the parking lot?

13:52.550 --> 13:53.120
[Xu Miyu]

13:53.440 --> 13:54.200
I've searched everywhere.

13:53.540 --> 13:57.000
[Luo Qingping]

13:54.200 --> 13:55.030
Nothing.

14:00.090 --> 14:00.920
I see.

14:00.960 --> 14:02.250
Thanks, everyone.

14:02.600 --> 14:04.480
[Xu Miyu]

14:15.910 --> 14:16.790
Mr. Tan.

14:17.230 --> 14:18.090
Did you find it?

14:23.800 --> 14:25.510
Maybe fate was trying to tell me all along

14:25.510 --> 14:28.180
that this painting
just wasn't meant to be shown.

14:28.180 --> 14:28.960
It's fine.

14:31.740 --> 14:33.540
I'm sorry, Mr. Tan.

14:34.240 --> 14:36.390
I didn't know
that to hold an exhibition at Purong,

14:36.390 --> 14:37.650
you lost so much money.

14:38.880 --> 14:41.810
In the end,
I still failed your expectations.

14:41.840 --> 14:43.610
No, I was too greedy.

14:43.910 --> 14:46.570
I always want the best result
in everything I do.

14:46.840 --> 14:47.440
It's fine.

14:47.550 --> 14:49.670
Fortunately, you are its first audience,

14:49.670 --> 14:50.600
so it's worth it.

15:00.440 --> 15:01.320
Mr. Tan,

15:01.810 --> 15:02.480
this painting, "Years",

15:02.480 --> 15:05.010
hasn't been exhibited
anywhere else, right?

15:06.290 --> 15:07.550
Do you have any other works

15:07.550 --> 15:09.960
in Shanghai that haven't been
exhibited yet?

15:09.960 --> 15:10.550
Yes.

15:11.000 --> 15:12.860
They are all at my friend's place.

15:14.690 --> 15:16.930
You mean

15:16.960 --> 15:19.860
that you want to replace this piece
with one of my other paintings

15:19.860 --> 15:21.480
and still proceed
with the unveiling exhibition?

15:21.480 --> 15:23.320
We will keep looking for the painting,

15:23.320 --> 15:24.550
but as a backup plan,

15:24.550 --> 15:25.910
do you think this works?

15:27.350 --> 15:28.080
No.

15:28.110 --> 15:30.140
That painting deviates from
the theme of "Years".

15:30.140 --> 15:31.070
Absolutely not.

15:31.320 --> 15:32.920
My understanding of "Years"

15:32.940 --> 15:34.770
is not just the passage of time.

15:34.800 --> 15:36.640
It also includes everything

15:36.670 --> 15:39.670
created by the past—
its changes and reflections.

15:39.910 --> 15:40.840
It is, in fact,

15:40.840 --> 15:42.350
a very broad, all-encompassing theme.

15:42.350 --> 15:44.820
Every moment that once moved you

15:45.150 --> 15:47.270
can be considered your gilded years.

15:51.200 --> 15:53.360
But my friend is not in Shanghai
right now.

15:53.360 --> 15:55.000
We have to pick up the painting ourselves.

15:55.000 --> 15:56.340
And his place is very far away.

15:56.340 --> 15:58.170
Right now, we probably

15:58.200 --> 15:59.930
only have about an hour left.

15:59.950 --> 16:01.280
There's simply no time.

16:01.440 --> 16:03.420
How will you know if you don't try?

16:03.910 --> 16:04.750
Trust me.

16:15.300 --> 16:16.740
Xu Miyu went out.

16:21.850 --> 16:22.560
Went out?

16:23.580 --> 16:24.840
What is she going to do?

16:26.000 --> 16:27.670
Why do you care what she's doing?

16:27.670 --> 16:29.610
Even if she runs to America,

16:29.630 --> 16:31.560
she still won't find the painting.

16:32.810 --> 16:34.810
Seems they are truly at a dead end.

16:36.080 --> 16:37.290
It's about time.

16:37.310 --> 16:38.520
Let the media in.

16:38.680 --> 16:41.510
Time for us to escalate things.

16:48.020 --> 16:49.910
Sir, please drive faster.

16:49.910 --> 16:50.720
I'm in a hurry.

16:50.720 --> 16:51.200
Okay.

16:59.870 --> 17:02.350
We appreciate everyone's time today.

17:02.370 --> 17:05.230
Let's keep up the momentum
going for the next steps.

17:06.200 --> 17:06.690
Sure.

17:06.720 --> 17:07.520
Keep in touch.

17:07.849 --> 17:08.339
Bye.

17:09.150 --> 17:09.920
[Meeting is over]

17:17.349 --> 17:18.609
We talked all morning.

17:19.640 --> 17:20.960
We didn't reach any consensus.

17:20.960 --> 17:23.220
These foreigners are really something.

17:23.589 --> 17:26.050
It seems a trip to New Zealand
is inevitable.

17:31.240 --> 17:33.440
Something happened at the exhibition.

17:39.720 --> 17:40.520
Hello.

17:43.770 --> 17:44.860
["Gilded Years" Art Exhibition Media List]

17:44.890 --> 17:47.230
[Organization: Laiyi Media Co., Ltd.]
[Name: Zhao Xu]

17:50.580 --> 17:51.200
I'm sorry,

17:51.200 --> 17:51.960
Mr. Zhao.

17:52.540 --> 17:54.470
Your organization is not

17:54.490 --> 17:55.910
on my media list.

17:56.370 --> 17:58.770
It might not be convenient
to let you two in.

17:58.950 --> 18:01.130
Wait, did you miss the registration?

18:02.250 --> 18:03.550
I have a media permit.

18:03.570 --> 18:05.300
It has your leader's stamp on it.

18:04.350 --> 18:06.310
[Media Filming Permit]

18:06.880 --> 18:07.790
Or is it

18:07.810 --> 18:09.530
that Mr. Wei's stamp

18:09.560 --> 18:10.620
is no longer valid?

18:11.930 --> 18:13.090
How could that be?

18:14.720 --> 18:15.400
In terms of publicity,

18:15.400 --> 18:17.400
please put in a good word
for us, Mr. Zhao.

18:17.400 --> 18:18.400
Please follow me.

18:41.440 --> 18:43.030
Then we'll see.

18:43.800 --> 18:45.200
Everything is arranged.

18:46.440 --> 18:47.000
Mr. Ji.

18:48.040 --> 18:48.520
Mr. Ji.

18:49.270 --> 18:51.000
I haven't seen you all morning.

18:51.290 --> 18:53.050
I heard there was a little problem.

18:53.050 --> 18:54.810
Ms. Xu has gone missing.

18:54.840 --> 18:55.640
Is it serious?

18:55.830 --> 18:57.370
Thank you for your concern, Mr. Wei.

18:57.370 --> 18:59.610
You even came in person to support us.

18:59.630 --> 19:00.970
With you here,
it'd be hard to mess things up.

19:00.970 --> 19:02.540
How can I support you?

19:02.570 --> 19:03.390
I don't know anything about art.

19:03.390 --> 19:04.390
I'm just a layman.

19:04.440 --> 19:05.920
I'm just here to join the fun,

19:05.920 --> 19:07.550
to see if there are any problems,

19:07.550 --> 19:09.070
so I can lend a hand.

19:10.820 --> 19:11.910
Please come in.

19:12.020 --> 19:12.430
Here,

19:12.480 --> 19:13.070
please.

19:49.440 --> 19:50.520
Mr. Tan,

19:51.130 --> 19:52.200
it's time.

19:52.220 --> 19:53.350
Aren't we starting?

19:59.450 --> 20:01.100
Okay, let's start.

20:01.160 --> 20:01.700
Okay.

20:07.280 --> 20:09.310
Three, two, one.

20:32.020 --> 20:35.250
[Gilded Years,
Tan Jizhou's Shanghai Art Exhibition]

20:34.520 --> 20:35.410
Please.

20:35.540 --> 20:38.960
[Gilded Years,
Tan Jizhou's Shanghai Art Exhibition]

20:45.960 --> 20:48.110
The images you're seeing now

20:48.110 --> 20:50.110
are a presentation of old Shanghai.

20:50.400 --> 20:52.110
Because our theme is "Years".

20:52.110 --> 20:55.750
So I hope that through this installation,

20:55.750 --> 20:58.000
everyone can feel the passage

20:58.080 --> 20:59.610
and changes of time.

21:00.350 --> 21:01.350
You can go inside.

21:04.550 --> 21:07.070
On both sides are my paintings

21:07.070 --> 21:09.030
and some photos of old Shanghai.

21:13.350 --> 21:16.070
And as we keep moving forward,

21:16.550 --> 21:18.510
we arrive at modern Shanghai.

21:28.160 --> 21:29.350
So life is probably like this—

21:29.350 --> 21:30.830
while we are walking,

21:30.830 --> 21:32.560
time has already slipped away.

21:32.720 --> 21:33.180
Please,

21:33.630 --> 21:34.160
this way.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.640
Come on in, everyone.

21:49.510 --> 21:51.400
In fact, for this art exhibition,

21:52.160 --> 21:53.350
we've made some adjustments

21:53.350 --> 21:54.960
to the space as well,

21:55.160 --> 21:56.920
all to better fit our theme.

21:57.200 --> 21:58.400
Our theme is relatively

21:58.400 --> 21:59.720
fluid.

21:59.750 --> 22:02.210
It's not meant to feel rigid
or overly fixed.

22:02.970 --> 22:03.780
This way.

22:11.150 --> 22:14.730
[Xu Miyu]

22:14.200 --> 22:15.000
Where are you?

22:21.970 --> 22:24.140
Sir, I'll get off here.

22:53.230 --> 22:54.160
The theme of our exhibition this time

22:54.160 --> 22:57.460
explores the relationship
between time and self.

22:58.480 --> 23:01.920
And this painting, "Gaze",
is the culmination of this theme.

23:02.360 --> 23:05.560
We often feel the passage
of time through our eyes.

23:05.580 --> 23:07.310
There are many eyes in the painting.

23:07.310 --> 23:09.330
They are not only the gaze
of the outside world on us,

23:09.330 --> 23:11.230
but also at different ages,

23:11.250 --> 23:12.580
our self-examination.

23:12.890 --> 23:14.160
At the same time, it also tells the story

23:14.160 --> 23:15.540
of how we

23:15.570 --> 23:17.050
coexist with ourselves

23:17.070 --> 23:18.670
at different stages of life.

23:20.160 --> 23:20.880
Mr. Tan,

23:20.900 --> 23:22.360
you previously announced

23:22.400 --> 23:23.750
that the exhibition would premiere

23:23.750 --> 23:26.820
your never-before-seen new work "Years",

23:26.840 --> 23:29.720
so why has it suddenly been changed to
"Gaze" instead?

23:29.720 --> 23:30.400
Yes.

23:30.780 --> 23:33.820
This is actually a minor adjustment

23:33.900 --> 23:36.740
my team and I made
during the exhibition setup.

23:37.250 --> 23:40.010
We believe that "Years"
is all-encompassing.

23:40.030 --> 23:43.220
Rather than challenging its
indescribable image,

23:43.250 --> 23:45.060
it's better to take a different approach

23:45.060 --> 23:46.400
and use a more inclusive

23:46.400 --> 23:50.240
and emotional way
to tell my understanding.

23:50.750 --> 23:51.640
Mr. Tan,

23:52.160 --> 23:53.480
many of us here today

23:53.480 --> 23:56.240
came here to see the true face of "Years."

23:56.270 --> 23:58.160
Even if for the sake of effect,

23:58.160 --> 23:59.960
you adjusted the main exhibits,

24:00.160 --> 24:02.240
the unveiling of "Years"
is still highly anticipated.

24:02.240 --> 24:02.830
Thank you.

24:02.830 --> 24:05.640
Then may I ask why you didn't exhibit it?

24:06.110 --> 24:06.590
Sorry.

24:06.590 --> 24:07.590
I think I said it.

24:07.590 --> 24:09.480
"Years" is not suitable
for this exhibition.

24:09.480 --> 24:13.080
Is it not suitable for exhibition
or is it unable to be exhibited?

24:14.160 --> 24:15.200
Rumor has it that

24:15.200 --> 24:17.920
you actually haven't finished
this painting.

24:18.740 --> 24:19.910
Not finished?

24:20.030 --> 24:21.800
That's sheer nonsense.

24:21.940 --> 24:23.770
Then why isn't it being shown?

24:23.790 --> 24:26.450
Or did something happen

24:26.480 --> 24:28.750
during the installation process—

24:28.750 --> 24:30.030
was there an incident caused
by improper handling at the hotel?

24:30.030 --> 24:32.960
No way. Did the hotel lose the painting?

24:59.780 --> 25:01.530
Dear journalist friends,

25:01.550 --> 25:03.730
please calm down.

25:03.750 --> 25:04.870
I urge everyone

25:04.900 --> 25:07.000
to give our general manager
of Purong Hotel,

25:07.000 --> 25:07.720
Mr. Ji,

25:07.740 --> 25:09.210
a little time,

25:09.240 --> 25:11.960
and let him explain

25:11.980 --> 25:12.900
the current situation to everyone.

25:12.900 --> 25:13.740
Okay?

25:13.960 --> 25:15.070
Mr. Ji, please.

25:20.830 --> 25:22.160
Friends from the media,

25:22.590 --> 25:24.050
Mr. Tan has already stated

25:24.680 --> 25:26.070
that the painting cannot be exhibited

25:26.070 --> 25:27.270
due to personal reasons.

25:27.270 --> 25:29.450
And as the general manager of the venue,

25:29.450 --> 25:30.610
I assure everyone

25:30.640 --> 25:32.130
that the hotel did not

25:32.150 --> 25:34.470
mishandle the exhibits.

25:34.640 --> 25:37.600
Then bring the painting
out for display now.

25:37.960 --> 25:38.960
Now!

25:38.960 --> 25:39.510
Yes.

25:39.510 --> 25:40.110
He's right.

25:40.110 --> 25:41.530
Bring it out for us to see.

25:43.880 --> 25:45.230
Let us see it.

25:46.500 --> 25:48.650
Since you're looking forward to this work,

25:48.650 --> 25:49.850
we have no reason

25:49.880 --> 25:51.550
to let you down.

25:52.530 --> 25:54.730
Mr. Tan, you have no objections, right?

25:55.240 --> 25:55.880
I...

26:27.730 --> 26:29.170
This interlude

26:29.270 --> 26:31.440
is also a special opening

26:31.460 --> 26:32.670
of this exhibition.

26:32.880 --> 26:33.720
Time passes

26:33.720 --> 26:34.960
and cannot be retrieved.

26:34.960 --> 26:37.030
But as long as we keep passion
in our hearts,

26:37.030 --> 26:39.190
what is lost will eventually

26:39.210 --> 26:40.860
return to our lives

26:41.680 --> 26:43.100
at times we least expect.

27:16.010 --> 27:18.630
[Half an hour ago]

27:39.920 --> 27:41.780
Are you looking for the painting?

27:49.380 --> 27:51.240
Before being arranged
in the exhibition hall,

27:51.240 --> 27:53.340
all exhibits are kept in the storage room.

27:53.340 --> 27:54.880
The three cameras
inside and outside the room

27:54.880 --> 27:55.830
have also been checked,

27:55.830 --> 27:56.860
and there are no problems.

27:56.860 --> 27:58.480
The security department
will also arrange personnel

27:58.480 --> 28:00.290
to stand guard
and patrol around the clock.

28:00.290 --> 28:03.050
We guarantee that
wherever the exhibits are, they will be.

28:03.050 --> 28:04.100
Thanks for your hard work,

28:04.100 --> 28:04.820
Ms. Lu.

28:13.350 --> 28:15.640
Are you from the Engineering Department?

28:15.640 --> 28:16.970
What are you doing here?

28:18.400 --> 28:19.090
Nothing.

28:19.320 --> 28:20.790
I just came to see

28:20.810 --> 28:22.530
when the exhibits
will enter the exhibition hall.

28:22.530 --> 28:23.990
I'll get back to work then.

28:25.640 --> 28:26.400
You two,

28:26.400 --> 28:29.060
don't press the paintings.
Stand them upright.

28:37.840 --> 28:39.270
Those paintings are all wrapped in cloth.

28:39.270 --> 28:40.650
I can't tell which is which.

28:40.650 --> 28:42.250
How am I supposed to steal it?

28:42.710 --> 28:43.510
Okay.

28:43.890 --> 28:45.480
Let's wait until it's on the wall.

28:45.480 --> 28:46.590
Let's be clear—

28:46.720 --> 28:48.020
we had an agreement.
The money you promised me

28:48.020 --> 28:49.680
can only go up, not down.

28:49.810 --> 28:51.210
No problem. Don't worry.

28:57.430 --> 28:59.030
They really are up to no good.

28:59.290 --> 29:00.950
Should we secure them now?

29:01.400 --> 29:02.070
No rush.

29:02.520 --> 29:03.730
Nothing has happened yet.

29:03.730 --> 29:05.030
Catching them now is useless.

29:05.030 --> 29:06.610
It might just tip them off.

29:07.350 --> 29:08.210
We might as well

29:08.800 --> 29:11.860
play along and let them take the bait,

29:12.070 --> 29:13.310
and we will swoop in.

29:20.410 --> 29:27.040
[Engineering Department]

29:31.710 --> 29:34.100
[Engineering Department]

29:46.640 --> 29:47.540
Surprised?

29:48.510 --> 29:50.240
Your so-called foolproof plan

29:50.400 --> 29:51.860
has already been cracked.

29:53.730 --> 29:55.470
The reason we didn't expose you right away

29:54.790 --> 30:00.950
[Engineering Department]

29:55.720 --> 29:56.790
was just to see

29:57.310 --> 29:59.550
what tricks the mastermind was playing

29:59.960 --> 30:01.360
and catch you all at once.

30:01.590 --> 30:02.850
That engineer from
the Engineering Department, Qin Ming,

30:02.850 --> 30:04.850
has already confessed everything.

30:05.310 --> 30:07.230
He said it was you, Director Qian,

30:07.920 --> 30:10.250
who instructed him to steal the painting,

30:10.680 --> 30:13.930
and that you also planted your own people
in the security department

30:13.930 --> 30:15.300
to create gaps

30:15.330 --> 30:16.550
and sabotage the cameras.

30:16.550 --> 30:17.750
It was all your doing.

30:20.110 --> 30:20.680
Mr. Ji,

30:21.370 --> 30:24.940
he is obviously making wild accusations
out of desperation.

30:25.480 --> 30:25.920
What?

30:26.680 --> 30:28.340
You believe someone like him?

30:28.750 --> 30:30.610
Can his words be used as evidence?

30:30.920 --> 30:32.080
Then, Director Qian,

30:32.080 --> 30:34.410
see if this can be used as evidence.

30:37.800 --> 30:39.770
I've sent everyone away.

30:40.370 --> 30:42.550
Go get the painting out right now.

30:43.010 --> 30:44.120
After it's done,

30:44.480 --> 30:46.700
you'll definitely get your reward.

30:48.540 --> 30:50.500
Well... How is this possible?

30:50.720 --> 30:53.100
This is the call record Qin Ming kept

30:53.130 --> 30:55.530
to prevent you
from going back on your word.

30:58.500 --> 30:59.410
Mr. Wei,

30:59.830 --> 31:00.550
help me.

31:03.880 --> 31:04.830
Shut up!

31:05.920 --> 31:08.340
Qian Xun, you're so foolish.

31:09.110 --> 31:09.790
How could you do something

31:09.790 --> 31:11.470
so harmful to the hotel?

31:12.310 --> 31:13.310
I'm so disappointed in you.

31:13.310 --> 31:14.380
You brought this upon yourself.

31:14.380 --> 31:15.480
You've completely embarrassed me.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.000
Mr. Wei.

31:16.030 --> 31:16.470
I...

31:17.030 --> 31:18.270
Since both the art thief

31:18.270 --> 31:20.160
and the mastermind have been caught,

31:20.160 --> 31:21.230
just handle it as you see fit.

31:21.230 --> 31:21.910
No.

31:22.440 --> 31:23.950
You must deal with this severely.

31:23.950 --> 31:25.130
Don't worry about my pride.

31:25.130 --> 31:27.160
Mr. Wei, how could we not consider you?

31:27.160 --> 31:29.090
We haven't finished speaking yet.

31:33.860 --> 31:34.320
[Tan Jizhou Solo Art Exhibition]

31:34.340 --> 31:34.800
[Major security breach reported
at Purong Hotel during the event]

31:34.950 --> 31:36.760
[Tan Jizhou solo exhibition
held at Purong Hotel]

31:35.770 --> 31:37.400
These false reports

31:36.790 --> 31:38.400
[On-site: Severe security failure
at the venue]

31:37.430 --> 31:40.380
have made Ms. Lin and Mr. Tan very angry.

31:40.610 --> 31:41.630
What's stranger is

31:41.630 --> 31:42.310
that this media outlet

31:42.310 --> 31:44.070
wasn't even on our invitation list.

31:44.070 --> 31:46.800
But their reporter Zhao Xu
appeared at the scene,

31:46.830 --> 31:48.590
kept steering the narrative,

31:48.590 --> 31:50.550
and wouldn't let go of the issue
with Mr. Tan's painting.

31:50.550 --> 31:52.080
Is this also a coincidence?

31:55.890 --> 31:57.540
What does this prove?

31:58.030 --> 31:58.790
It's obviously a

31:58.790 --> 32:00.880
sketchy media outlet fishing
in troubled waters.

32:00.880 --> 32:02.160
Shouldn't we just have them take down

32:02.160 --> 32:03.550
the false press release?

32:03.550 --> 32:04.510
But coincidentally,

32:04.510 --> 32:07.030
the time they published
the article was 10:05.

32:07.030 --> 32:08.750
Including the ribbon-cutting ceremony,

32:08.750 --> 32:10.310
the exhibition hall didn't officially open

32:10.310 --> 32:11.830
until after 10:10 AM.

32:12.710 --> 32:13.780
I don't know how this media outlet

32:13.780 --> 32:15.580
could predict the future,

32:15.610 --> 32:18.260
knowing Mr. Tan's
new painting would be a no-show.

32:18.260 --> 32:18.910
Also,

32:19.440 --> 32:21.110
why is Mr. Wei's seal

32:21.440 --> 32:23.640
on this media permit?

32:22.960 --> 32:25.060
[Media Filming Permit] [Wei Siyuan Seal]

32:25.750 --> 32:26.950
Can you explain this?

32:35.870 --> 32:37.220
It really is my seal.

32:39.530 --> 32:41.920
It's my fault
for trusting the wrong people.

32:41.920 --> 32:43.030
In just one day,

32:43.800 --> 32:46.230
two good brothers betrayed me.

32:47.310 --> 32:48.410
It breaks my heart.

32:51.110 --> 32:52.070
My seal has actually been kept

32:52.070 --> 32:54.400
by Mr. Huang from the finance department.

32:54.750 --> 32:57.150
Who would have thought
he'd use it for this.

32:58.080 --> 32:59.810
It's my failure in management.

33:04.110 --> 33:04.640
What?

33:06.180 --> 33:07.380
You don't believe me?

33:08.160 --> 33:09.310
If you don't believe me, go check.

33:09.310 --> 33:10.770
Feel free to investigate.

33:15.350 --> 33:16.000
[Where are you?]

33:16.020 --> 33:16.810
[Go back to the hotel now.]

33:16.840 --> 33:17.740
[Don't act rashly.]

33:17.770 --> 33:18.640
[Trust me.]

33:28.980 --> 33:29.740
Miyu.

33:31.230 --> 33:31.910
Miyu.

33:36.210 --> 33:37.510
So you knew from the beginning

33:37.510 --> 33:38.500
that the painting wasn't lost,

33:38.500 --> 33:40.500
but you didn't tell me a word, right?

33:40.570 --> 33:42.430
I really didn't mean to lie to you.

33:43.190 --> 33:43.990
It was them.

33:44.010 --> 33:46.230
They were determined to
ruin this exhibition.

33:46.230 --> 33:47.550
If we didn't play along

33:47.550 --> 33:48.590
to dispel their doubts

33:48.590 --> 33:49.750
and catch them all at once,

33:49.750 --> 33:51.000
we would only be more passive.

33:51.000 --> 33:52.050
What do you mean?

33:52.070 --> 33:53.750
So watching me act like a clown

33:53.750 --> 33:54.310
running around,

33:54.310 --> 33:56.290
was that also part of your plan?

33:56.640 --> 33:57.310
Ji Feng,

33:57.830 --> 33:58.750
is there not even this basic trust

33:58.750 --> 34:00.310
between the two of us?

34:01.310 --> 34:03.070
Is it so hard to just discuss it with me?

34:03.070 --> 34:04.490
If I had discussed it with you,

34:04.490 --> 34:06.290
would you have agreed to my plan?

34:13.199 --> 34:14.340
I know you too well.

34:15.130 --> 34:16.440
You wouldn't have agreed.

34:16.440 --> 34:17.130
Yes.

34:17.400 --> 34:19.800
I would never risk our clients' interests.

34:20.540 --> 34:21.320
I suddenly realized

34:21.320 --> 34:22.850
that I don't know you at all.

34:23.110 --> 34:24.230
I used to think

34:24.230 --> 34:25.510
you just looked unreasonable,

34:25.510 --> 34:27.940
but I didn't expect you
to be truly cold-blooded.

34:27.940 --> 34:29.190
You are the general manager of the hotel.

34:29.190 --> 34:30.650
You have your big picture.

34:30.670 --> 34:31.800
But do Mr. Tan and I

34:31.800 --> 34:35.110
-deserve to be pawns in your game?
-I never thought about it...

34:35.110 --> 34:36.880
I really never thought about
ruining that art exhibition.

34:36.880 --> 34:38.730
Did you ever consider my feelings?

34:38.730 --> 34:40.989
Have you considered Mr. Tan's position?

34:41.280 --> 34:42.190
Because of his trust in the hotel

34:42.190 --> 34:43.070
and in us,

34:43.070 --> 34:44.880
how much pressure
and risk has he taken on?

34:44.880 --> 34:46.710
You used his exhibition as a target

34:46.710 --> 34:49.370
-to get rid of your dissidents.
-So you're angry

34:49.520 --> 34:51.440
-Did you respect him?
-because I used you,

34:51.440 --> 34:52.590
or because you did this case

34:52.590 --> 34:53.880
just for Tan Jizhou?

35:14.000 --> 35:15.800
Let's both think about it again.

35:15.810 --> 35:17.470
Let's both calm down for a bit.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.950
♪ I know at the start of every story ♪

35:21.990 --> 35:24.010
♪ They all feel somewhat the same ♪

35:25.880 --> 35:28.070
♪ Just never thought I would ♪

35:28.980 --> 35:31.110
♪ Fall for you so deeply ♪

35:32.810 --> 35:35.210
♪ Why did I have to lose myself? ♪

35:35.780 --> 35:37.890
♪ In the virtual world ♪

35:39.270 --> 35:44.480
♪ Unfinished dreams hurt the most ♪

35:46.210 --> 35:47.840
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

35:48.610 --> 35:51.850
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

35:53.500 --> 35:55.010
♪ Until I met you ♪

35:55.900 --> 35:59.100
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

35:59.630 --> 36:01.410
♪ For your dream ♪

36:01.730 --> 36:03.460
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

36:04.090 --> 36:06.290
♪ Love really hurts ♪

36:07.520 --> 36:12.180
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

36:14.730 --> 36:23.020
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

36:23.440 --> 36:25.150
Mr. Ji, are you looking for me?

36:25.150 --> 36:25.870
Mr. Tan.

36:26.710 --> 36:27.510
Well,

36:27.510 --> 36:29.760
an unexpected accident
occurred during your art exhibition,

36:29.760 --> 36:31.520
which has caused a negative impact on you.

36:31.520 --> 36:32.980
We are very sorry for that.

36:33.400 --> 36:35.190
It's fine. Come on in.

36:35.210 --> 36:36.120
It's okay.

36:37.000 --> 36:38.200
I just want to tell you

36:38.710 --> 36:41.130
that the accident
has entered the investigation stage,

36:41.130 --> 36:43.360
and the relevant persons in charge
have been found.

36:43.360 --> 36:44.710
As soon as there are any results,

36:44.710 --> 36:46.550
I will update you immediately.

36:47.070 --> 36:47.590
Okay.

36:53.510 --> 36:54.570
Frankly speaking,

36:54.840 --> 36:56.110
during this process,

36:56.550 --> 36:58.290
my concealment

36:58.510 --> 36:59.550
has caused unnecessary risks and worries

36:59.550 --> 37:02.070
to you and your team.

37:02.900 --> 37:05.440
I sincerely apologize to you.

37:07.030 --> 37:08.400
Thank you for your honesty, Mr. Ji.

37:08.400 --> 37:10.620
I accept your apology.

37:11.710 --> 37:14.360
Okay. I won't disturb your rest then.

37:14.360 --> 37:14.920
Okay.

37:16.370 --> 37:17.060
Mr. Ji.

37:21.590 --> 37:23.430
I've heard about

37:23.510 --> 37:25.420
the bet between Purong and Kuanli.

37:25.420 --> 37:27.080
Miyu, at such a critical moment,

37:27.080 --> 37:28.980
is trying her best
to facilitate this cooperation.

37:28.980 --> 37:31.280
Mr. Ji, you must know why.

37:33.680 --> 37:35.050
Mr. Tan, what you want to say is...

37:35.050 --> 37:35.850
Nothing.

37:36.230 --> 37:38.710
I... I just don't want her to be let down.

37:39.410 --> 37:41.370
I don't want any other reasons

37:41.670 --> 37:43.060
to make you misunderstand
her original intention.

37:43.060 --> 37:44.710
To her and your relationship,

37:44.710 --> 37:46.240
I think it would be harmful.

37:48.260 --> 37:50.260
Thank you for the reminder, Mr. Tan.

37:50.360 --> 37:51.190
But,

37:51.360 --> 37:53.160
the matter between Xu Miyu and me

37:54.260 --> 37:55.660
is none of your business.

37:58.360 --> 37:58.880
Okay.

38:14.480 --> 38:15.720
Hello.

38:15.820 --> 38:16.550
Excuse me.

38:16.550 --> 38:18.040
Sorry to take up your time.

38:18.060 --> 38:19.610
I have a few words to say.

38:20.720 --> 38:22.440
First of all, thank you.

38:22.550 --> 38:24.550
I really have so many people to thank

38:24.630 --> 38:27.140
because you've been with me all the way.

38:27.480 --> 38:28.760
But due to time constraints,

38:28.760 --> 38:30.960
I can't name all of you today.

38:30.980 --> 38:32.260
But please believe me,

38:32.550 --> 38:34.300
you are always in my heart.

38:34.440 --> 38:35.040
Thank you.

38:45.070 --> 38:46.360
This moment tonight

38:46.360 --> 38:47.560
belongs not only to me

38:47.570 --> 38:48.860
and my team,

38:49.190 --> 38:51.550
but also to a special person.

38:52.190 --> 38:53.190
Because she is the one

38:53.190 --> 38:54.800
who created this moment.

38:55.320 --> 38:56.030
So next,

38:56.030 --> 38:58.440
please give your warmest applause.

38:58.440 --> 38:59.480
I would like to invite my friend,

38:59.480 --> 39:00.960
Ms. Xu Miyu, to the stage.

39:00.960 --> 39:01.560
Thank you.

39:14.720 --> 39:15.880
Excuse me.

39:17.960 --> 39:18.920
Ms. Xu is

39:18.920 --> 39:21.110
the venue manager for my exhibition.

39:21.930 --> 39:23.550
It's fair to say that without her support,

39:23.550 --> 39:26.410
there wouldn't be today's
meaningful exhibition.

39:33.070 --> 39:34.070
So,

39:34.090 --> 39:35.460
Miyu, thank you.

39:35.490 --> 39:36.980
Thank you for your meticulous care,

39:36.980 --> 39:39.100
and your full dedication.

39:39.220 --> 39:41.500
I believe it will be hard for me to forget

39:41.550 --> 39:45.080
this exhibition full of
surprises and sincerity.

39:45.880 --> 39:46.960
Inviting you on stage

39:46.960 --> 39:48.790
is not just to thank you.

39:48.920 --> 39:50.800
Actually, I have a small request.

39:53.000 --> 39:56.030
Because this is our first cooperation.

39:56.940 --> 39:59.000
But I don't want it to be the last time.

39:59.360 --> 40:00.480
I hope we can create

40:00.480 --> 40:01.630
more next time

40:02.030 --> 40:03.560
and create more surprises.

40:03.680 --> 40:04.440
Can we?

40:08.110 --> 40:08.760
Yes.

40:09.320 --> 40:10.000
Thank you.
